This is funny arcade game, based on the very old principle
of Scorched Tanks. Found on Atari consoles and arcade machines.

This is beta preview release, and many, MANY new features
will be added before released in full version.

Visit the homepage of HellHound SG on http://hellhound.nl.eu.org

Have fun with this one!


